  "text": "Protein A beads (50 mL slurry) were coated and cross-linked with 5 mg of anti-human L3 antibody (Abnova), previously shown to react specifically with T. brucei L3 [CITATION_1] . Procyclic cell extracts (100 mg) were incubated with the beads at 4uC overnight with rotation. The supernatant was tested for L3 and tubulin by western blot analysis and analyzed using the immunoprecipitation protocol described above for an interaction between L5 and P34/ P37.",
